@startuml
title ElectroCorp Web App - Energy Monitoring Frontend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "Energy Monitoring Frontend Bounded Context" {
  class "Domain" as Frontend_energy_monitoring_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Application" as Frontend_energy_monitoring_Application <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Frontend_energy_monitoring_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Presentation" as Frontend_energy_monitoring_Presentation <<layer>>
}

Frontend_energy_monitoring_Presentation ..> Frontend_energy_monitoring_Application : user actions / state
Frontend_energy_monitoring_Application ..> Frontend_energy_monitoring_Domain : models and rules
Frontend_energy_monitoring_Application ..> Frontend_energy_monitoring_Infrastructure : API services / adapters
Frontend_energy_monitoring_Infrastructure ..> Frontend_energy_monitoring_Domain : resources and mappers
Frontend_energy_monitoring_Presentation ..> Frontend_energy_monitoring_Domain : view models

note bottom of Frontend_energy_monitoring_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/frontend/layers/energy-monitoring.
end note

@enduml
